<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77c9ee5a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460s–13"><num value="460s–13">§ 460s–13.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated not more than $6,873,000 for the acquisition of lands and interests in land in connection with, and not more than $6,348,000 for development of, the Pictured Rocks National Lakeshore.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77c9ee5b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/668/s14">Pub. L. 89–668, § 14</ref>, <date date="1966-10-15">Oct. 15, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/925">80 Stat. 925</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
